summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for, the payment of the cost and expense of the condemnation of West 44th Place, from the intersection of 11th Avenue Northwest and West 44th Street to West 45th Street, and for the establishing of the curb grades thereof, and for the necessary slopes for cuts and fills upon the property abutting thereon, as provided in Ordinance No. 49984 of the City of Seattle, and repealing Ordinance No. 53111.
